contentitemdata.kenticocommunity.newslet.EmailSubject: The excitement 🤩 of Xperience by Kentico's roadmap with Brian McKeiver
contentitemdata.kenticocommunity.newslet.NewsletterEmailIntroContent:
Hey {!ResolveDynamicText("Recipient.FirstName","friend")!} ,

We're a little light on news from Kentico this week since we've been hard at work preparing for our partner Connection events.

However we do have an interview with Kentico MVP Brian McKeiver about Xperience by Kentico's roadmap, some information you might have missed if you are a new subscriber, and plenty of great content from the Kentico community. Enjoy!
contentitemdata.kenticocommunity.newslet.NewsletterEmailOutroContent: If you found the information in this newsletter helpful, something looks strange in your email client, or you have news, a video, or blot post to feature in a future newsletter - let us know by giving us some feedback.
